name: Screechers of the Xanthean Oasis
description: Hailing from the absurd Xanthan Forest, where the small is big and the big is small, the Screechers of the Xanthean Oasis are known to frequent Cinderkeep and consort with the mad wizard Zephyrial. Now residing atop the oasis crabs of Kathoon, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
